{"tid":48983,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"梁振英下午報名參選特首。","createTime":"2016-12-21T11:38:54.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-22T11:46:46.000Z","uid":28309,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cb729039b6d72f022ad274f6b26dbb8c61919031","tid":48983,"uid":28309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T11:38:54.000Z","msg":"行政長官參選人梁振英，下午會報名參選特首。<br />\n<br />\n梁振英下午3時，會到灣仔海港中心的選舉事務處提交提名表參選。競選辦主席張震遠和競選辦主任羅范椒芬，將會陪同交表。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，工聯會和民建聯分別有支持者提名給他，專業界別的選委亦相信是他的票倉。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=26242\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D26242&d=eoZ9JVL%2BtjW%2Fct7L%2B9eB4mN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=a88700c4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D26242&h=d5163b74\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=26242</a>"},{"pid":"1e96757f2bdd1422672bf97729f0e46ea5b10ed4","tid":48983,"uid":6992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T11:39:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13b26a29a8bd7bd5b86204c7c01c73f4be61e9bb","tid":48983,"uid":3650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T11:39:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1eedcb93ee1b3905a496700cfec003d65907842f","tid":48983,"uid":2022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T11:39:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bd29adf04aec8bbe7376b9a4bef3231e3b9511f3","tid":48983,"uid":27731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T11:42:06.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">其實樓主係咪覺得自己好撚風趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？</span></span>"},{"pid":"e79299bc18b368c8a7b1398abc81721bdb942eab","tid":48983,"uid":10726,